# Keep Docker build contexts small & secret-free.
# Applies to the repo-root build context (the Hono image).
**/node_modules
**/.venv
**/venv
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/cdk.out
**/coverage
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.pytest_cache
.git
.gitignore
# Never bake secrets into an image — env is injected at runtime via env_file.
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
LinodeVM
